  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While mastering the art of mop skating, you uncover the untidy secrets of a world obsessed with grime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/90669c476df3a4eebe46db53243bf3ad.poster.avif?t=1741042466\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/90669c476df3a4eebe46db53243bf3ad.webm?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/90669c476df3a4eebe46db53243bf3ad.mp4?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you skate, clean, and combo your way through chaotic environments, you’ll discover layers of mystery hidden beneath the dirt. Each level offers creative challenges and surprising twists that turn a simple cleaning gig into an unforgettable journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/cd3cdcc91a53b49b8a7d49b65584583d.poster.avif?t=1741042466\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/cd3cdcc91a53b49b8a7d49b65584583d.webm?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/cd3cdcc91a53b49b8a7d49b65584583d.mp4?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the fans of Jet Set Radio, PowerWash Simulator and Snake.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean, skate, and trick your way through hilariously dirty environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform wild combos and unlock creative mops to make cleaning more stylish than ever.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed boosts, extra-dirty spots, and challenging obstacles provide endless ways to approach each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase high scores while exploring quirky, interactive levels filled with surprising secrets and humor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessibility options for all players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying cleaning effects, mop tricks, and ridiculous combos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-depth mop customization!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/5193194bdc6cb5646578198e0d9619bb.poster.avif?t=1741042466\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/5193194bdc6cb5646578198e0d9619bb.webm?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/5193194bdc6cb5646578198e0d9619bb.mp4?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While mastering the art of mop skating, you uncover the untidy secrets of a world obsessed with grime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/90669c476df3a4eebe46db53243bf3ad.poster.avif?t=1741042466\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/90669c476df3a4eebe46db53243bf3ad.webm?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/90669c476df3a4eebe46db53243bf3ad.mp4?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you skate, clean, and combo your way through chaotic environments, you’ll discover layers of mystery hidden beneath the dirt. Each level offers creative challenges and surprising twists that turn a simple cleaning gig into an unforgettable journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/cd3cdcc91a53b49b8a7d49b65584583d.poster.avif?t=1741042466\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/cd3cdcc91a53b49b8a7d49b65584583d.webm?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/cd3cdcc91a53b49b8a7d49b65584583d.mp4?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the fans of Jet Set Radio, PowerWash Simulator and Snake.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean, skate, and trick your way through hilariously dirty environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform wild combos and unlock creative mops to make cleaning more stylish than ever.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed boosts, extra-dirty spots, and challenging obstacles provide endless ways to approach each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase high scores while exploring quirky, interactive levels filled with surprising secrets and humor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessibility options for all players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying cleaning effects, mop tricks, and ridiculous combos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-depth mop customization!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/5193194bdc6cb5646578198e0d9619bb.poster.avif?t=1741042466\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/5193194bdc6cb5646578198e0d9619bb.webm?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468230/extras/5193194bdc6cb5646578198e0d9619bb.mp4?t=1741042466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
